Registration

Important Notes:

  • There are no special discounts for any types of registrations. The registration fee is $100 for all attendees. The fee include admission to final paper uploading, technical sessions, workshops and tutorials, the conference proceedings.
  • For one submission, it should be ensured that one of the authors can finish the registration as the presenter before the event. For other attendees except the presenter, it is  free . Therefore only one registration is necessary for each accepted paper.
  • For the final submissions which length is beyond 6 pages, an additional surcharge of $100 per extra page has to be paid.
  • Registration is required to be finished before Xxx. xx, 2021.

Registration procedure is here

Cancellation Policy

  • In any cases, no refunds will be made if your registration is used to upload your final submission(s) for RCAR 2021.
  • To cancel your registration, please notify the secretariat by Email: ieee.rcar@gmail.com.
